- treatment_abiraterone x ar_v7_positive: adjusted risk-difference interaction 0.0118 (1.2 percentage points), p=0.2050
- treatment_docetaxel x visceral_mets: adjusted risk-difference interaction 0.0027 (0.3 percentage points), p=0.7828
- treatment_docetaxel x mcrpc: adjusted risk-difference interaction -0.0073 (-0.7 percentage points), p=0.3499
- treatment_pembrolizumab x autoimmune_disease: adjusted risk-difference interaction -0.0012 (-0.1 percentage points), p=0.9757
- treatment_olaparib x msi_high: adjusted risk-difference interaction -0.0480 (-4.8 percentage points), p=0.1604
